flowchart TB
    subgraph batchFlow [全量数据流DataX]
        Reader[Reader读取] --> Channel[Channel通道]
        Channel --> Writer[Writer写入]
    end

    subgraph streamFlow [增量数据流FlinkCDC]
        Binlog[Binlog日志] --> StoreComp[Store拉取]
        StoreComp --> FlinkJob[Flink CDC作业]
        FlinkJob --> TargetSink[写入目标库]
    end

    SourceDB[(源数据库)] --> Reader
    SourceDB --> Binlog
    Writer --> TargetDB[(目标数据库)]
    TargetSink --> TargetDB
